name: nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_t
desc: Options for configuring how expired DNS answers should be used.

items.name: var nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_default: nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_t
items.desc: Let the system determine whether or not to allow expired DNS answers.

items.name: var nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_allow: nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_t
items.desc: Explicitly allow the use of expired DNS answers.

items.name: var nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_prohibit: nw_parameters_expired_dns_behavior_t
items.desc: Explicitly prohibit the use of expired DNS answers.
